 * Brand logo (inline SVG).
 *
 * Uses `fill="currentColor"` so the logo colour follows the surrounding
 * text colour — dark on the white header, white on the dark footer.
 *
 * Lives in template-parts/ (which is deployed) rather than src/images/
 * (dev-only) so it renders identically in dev and production without the
 * Vite manifest.
 *
 * @param array $args {
 *     @type string $class  Extra CSS classes for the <svg> (e.g. sizing).
 * }
 */

